@func.belt_speed: (function(tpm,metric,tack){if(tack!=0){return tpm;} var speed= (231.0/tpm)*60; if (metric==0){return (speed*3.281).toFixed(1) + ' ft/min';}else{return speed.toFixed(1) + ' M/min'}})
@func.bit_array: (function(val){if(val == 0){return 0;}else{ var i = 0; while(i<16 && ((val>>i) & 1) == 0){ i++; } i++;  return i; } })
@func.password_hash: (function(phash){    var buf = Buffer.alloc(8); buf.writeUInt16LE(phash[1],0); buf.writeUInt16LE(phash[0],2); buf.writeUInt16LE(phash[2],6); buf.writeUInt16LE(phash[3],4);return buf;});
